{"tid":1869148,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"打牌導致肺炎 政治沒收一索","createTime":"2020-02-08T04:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T04:48:20.000Z","uid":279909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67726fa2dcc8fade66929ade03219c0666722f3a","tid":1869148,"uid":279909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"浙江寧波疫情防控發布會上特別通報一宗打麻雀聚集案例，1人打麻雀致多人感染武漢肺炎。衢州九華鄉鄉政府為阻止聚眾打麻雀，逐家上門勸說，兩天沒收了600多隻一索。<br />\n<br />\n官員指從寧波的確診個案看來，聚集事件和家庭及鄰里傳播為主要感染原因。九華鄉鄉政府宣傳委員鄭時華表示，農曆年時民眾打麻雀都是很正常，上門勸導人家別打麻雀時總有人不聽，後來就在會上提出不如沒收麻雀，民眾就暫時沒法打了。鄉政府其後展開「捕雀行動」，先在23個村沒收一索，其後再逐家逐戶沒收。<br />\n<br />\n工作人員表示，所有一索均有標註來自那條村，待疫情過後再發還給村民。<br />\n<br />\nFrom <a href=\"http://On.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOn.cc&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOiBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=95e4f567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">On.cc</a><br />\n<br />\n無得打牌了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dc0ff71b179c5ec759be29f41599ab1df85d32","tid":1869148,"uid":34854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"無一索照打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1513fedc2d698b61f831fb5d09acdc4146e0970e","tid":1869148,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87qu3pX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87qu3pX.jpg&h=7205249a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b70e013bd6372c2bd1b75e49d8c9569dc77f91f","tid":1869148,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5dc0ff71b179c5ec759be29f41599ab1df85d32","tid":1869148,"uid":34854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"無一索照打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:48:20.000Z","msg":"白牌當一索咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa